OL,3,CWater firm claims stake in woman's
OL,4,Chome after she stopped paying bills
OL,6,FA campaigner who has not paid her
OL,7,Fwater bill in five years has accused
OL,8,FSouth West Water of using scare
OL,9,Ftactics to get her to pay - after the
OL,10,Ffirm claimed a stake in her home.
OL,12,FImogen May, from Crediton in Devon,
OL,13,Fbelieves South West Water is not doing
OL,14,Fenough to clean up rivers and prevent
OL,15,Fsewage spills.
OL,17,FAs a form of protest, she has now
OL,18,Fwithheld her payments for five years
OL,19,Fand owes around #3,000.
