OL,6,F"I feel really sad," she told ITV News
OL,7,FWest Country. "I am passionate about
OL,8,Fthe natural world. I swim in the
OL,9,Frivers, I swim in the sea, my go-to
OL,10,Fwhenever I can is spend time near
OL,11,Fwater.
OL,13,F"It actually hurts me. It makes me
OL,14,Ffeel incredibly sad. I've got two
OL,15,Fwonderful daughters and I am doing
OL,16,Fthis to secure a future for them. They
OL,17,Fought not to be fighting when they
OL,18,Freach my age and I really hope that
OL,19,Fthey are not."
