OL,3,CWater firm claims stake in woman's
OL,4,Chome after she stopped paying bills
OL,6,FSouth West Water has now taken legal
OL,7,Faction to claim a stake in Imogen's
OL,8,Fhouse via the Land Registry. This
OL,9,Fmeans that, when the house is sold,
OL,10,Fthe company can take what it is owed.
OL,12,FImogen described this action as
OL,13,F"typical, standard behaviour" of "an
OL,14,Farrogant corporation in complete
OL,15,Fdenial of what they are doing to our
OL,16,Fecosystems and communities".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
