OL,6,FShe added: "They can have their money,
OL,7,Fwith goodwill, when they start
OL,8,Fspending it on what it is designed to
OL,9,Fbe spent on, as in clean water
OL,10,Fsupplies for all of us and clean
OL,11,Friverways, but they are not.
OL,13,F"They have all of the science, all of
OL,14,Fthe tech and resources at their
OL,15,Ffingertips to ensure that we have
OL,16,Fclean waterways and they are letting
OL,17,Fus down.
OL,19,F"Money is what they understand and it
OL,20,Fis the only way that we can get
OL,21,Fthrough to them."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
