OL,6,FFigures from the Environment Agency
OL,7,Fshow South West Water discharged
OL,8,Fsewage into rivers and seas 58,249
OL,9,Ftimes last year - up by more than 50%
OL,10,Fon 2022.
OL,12,FSouth West Water says it does not
OL,13,Fcomment on individual customer cases.
OL,15,FHowever, a spokesperson said: "We are
OL,16,Fserious about tackling storm overflows
OL,17,Fand change of this scale takes time,
OL,18,Fambition, and increased investment `
OL,19,Fand that is why we are investing
OL,20,F#850million in our region over two
OL,21,Fyears."
